OL,3,GEast
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FAny early cloud or mist patches
OL,6,Fwill likely fade away through the
OL,7,Fmorning. A largely sunny day then
OL,8,Ffollows, with light winds.
OL,9,
OL,10,CTonight:FSome higher cloud is likely
OL,11,Fto thicken from the west, however
OL,12,Foccasional clear spells will allow for
OL,13,Fsome mist or fog patches to develop by
OL,14,Fdawn. Mild with light winds.
OL,15,
OL,16,CThursday:FBrighter spells likely
OL,17,Fthrough the morning, mainly in the
OL,18,Feast, and soon feeling warm in any
OL,19,Fsunshine. Cloud then thickens further
OL,20,Fby the afternoon, with outbreaks of
OL,21,Frain likely later.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
