OL,3,GEast
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FChilly
OL,6,Fstart Friday then sunny intervals.
OL,7,FVariable cloud Saturday, perhaps some
OL,8,Fshowers, but also brighter intervals.
OL,9,FSunshine and showers Sunday.
OL,10,FTemperatures near normal for April,
OL,11,Fperhaps warmer on Saturday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
